                    PDEC(A;e,c,B)
[Polynomial decomposition. 
A is a polynomial in r variables, r>0.  A=x_r^e\cdot c+B.]
     safe PDEC.
(1)  [A=0?] if A=0 then {e:=0; c:=0; B:=0; return}.
(2)  [Decompose.] ADV2(A; e,c,B); if B=() then B:=0 ||
     
